node.text:
Does your #UPPAbabyVISTA need some TLC after all of your winter strolls ? Our Tune-UP Gear-UP Expert, Sam Osborne has all of the tips and tricks clean your VISTA wheels and keep you strolling smoothly all winter long!❄️ Tip: volume up!🔊
 
Looking for more info to help at-home Tune-UP's? Connect directly with our Tech Experts and schedule your virtual Tune-UP Gear-UP at the link in bio today!

node.title: ✨FEATURE FRIDAY✨ Tune-UP Gear-UP VISTA Cleaning at Home!

node.text:
✨FEATURE FRIDAY✨ Mid-July, hello sun!☀️😎 Protect your little one from the sun’s rays with the MESA Cabana Accessory. The Cabana has UPF protection and a wind/rain protection layer that easily folds out over your infant car seat for unexpected weather while on your strolls. Check out the end of the video to learn how to fold the accessory to store in your stroller’s basket!
 
❗️Important❗️This product is intended for strolling and transporting a child outdoors only. The Cabana must be removed from the MESA carrier while riding in a vehicle.

node.text:
🎨GIVEAWAY!🎨 We want to get your family ready to hit the road this summer with a chance to win one of three car seats from the UPPAbaby car seat family!

Three lucky artists, one from each category will be chosen to win a MESA, KNOX, or ALTA. Follow these simple steps below to enter:

1️⃣ Head over to the “Color Me Happy Giveaway” link in our bio.
2️⃣ Submit an original photo drawn by your child of their favorite family vacation or summertime activity. Parents with children too young to draw can submit on behalf of their little ones!
3️⃣Upload the original photo to the link in bio.

This giveaway is in no way sponsored or endorsed by Instagram or Gleam. Open to U.S. residents only. The giveaway ends 7/28/21 at 11:59 PM EST. The three winners will be chosen and contacted the week of 7/30/21. Good luck!

node.text:
✨FEATURE FRIDAY✨ Did you know the UPPAbaby CRUZ and VISTA strollers are designed with grey touchpoints that serve as visual indicators? They show that an adjustment is possible on buttons, tabs, and triggers. Whether it’s a reverse or recline of the seat, footrest positions, or extending the handlebar, these grey touchpoints help parents make adjustments to ensure a comfortable ride.

**Reminder! If you have the GREYSON or JAKE fashions, your strollers will have black touchpoints.

node.text:
✨FEATURE FRIDAY✨ Journey through the stages with the UPPAbaby Car Seat Family. We’ve got you covered from their ride first ride home to middle school drop-off!

 🔹MESA: Suitable for infants 4–35 lbs and up to 32” in height.
 🔹KNOX: Suitable for approximately 1–6 years old. Rear-facing: from 14–45 lbs, and using the included fit inlay from 14–25 lbs. Forward-facing: from 25–65 lbs. Height: up to 49″.
 🔹ALTA: Suitable from 40–100 lbs, and 38–57” in height. Approximately 6–10 years old.

node.text:
Let’s go Behind the Brand with Senior Design Engineer, Manpreet Singh Sokhi! Manpreet has been part of the team for over a year now. His role is to engineer and develop car seats, gather input and sprinkle a little magic of mathematics and science to bring ideas to life! Manpreet wanted to join the UPPAbaby team after he became a dad himself to his adorable son, Kavneer. He fell in love with the products and as they say, the rest is history!

A few fun facts about Manpreet:

 ▫️He has a strong passion for photography (and is great at it if we do say so ourselves!)
 ▫️ His favorite places to travel are Golden Temple, Amritsar, India!
 ▫️He is currently working on something SECRET! 🤫😉
